<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <meta name="description" content="A San Diego-based alt rock band.">
    <meta name=”robots” content="index">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/index.css"/>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{ faviconImg }}" >
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
</head>
<body class="flex flex-col justify-start items-center bg-black text-white font-primary">
<div class="flex flex-col justify-start items-center h-[4/5] lg:h-full w-screen bg-cover bg-center gap-6"
     style="background-image: url('{{ heroBackgroundImg }}')">
    <nav class="flex justify-center flex-row gap-4 mt-4">
        {% for nav in navs %}
            <a class="hover:outline-2 rounded-md py-1 px-2" href="{{ nav.link }}">{{ nav.name }}</a>
        {% endfor %}
    </nav>
    <img src="{{ logoImg }}" alt="logo" class="w-80 brightness-125"/>
    <h1 class="text-3xl text-shadow-md text-shadow-black">Debut album out now!</h1>
    <div class="w-120 hidden lg:block opacity-90">
        <iframe data-testid="embed-iframe" style="border-radius:12px"
                src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/4RlUQv73tjF6eYQaDqqxHK?utm_source=generator" width="100%"
                height="352" frameBorder="0" allowfullscreen=""
                allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
                loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
    <div class="w-90 lg:hidden opacity-90">
        <iframe data-testid="embed-iframe" style="border-radius:12px"
                src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/4RlUQv73tjF6eYQaDqqxHK?utm_source=generator" width="100%"
                height="152" frameBorder="0" allowfullscreen=""
                allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
                loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
    <div class="w-90 lg:w-120 opacity-85">
        <iframe style="border: 0; width: 100%; height: 120px;"
                src="https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=2746234876/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=63b2cc/tracklist=false/artwork=small/transparent=true/"
                seamless><a href="https://mishy.bandcamp.com/album/mishy">Mishy by Mishy</a></iframe>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-grow"></div>
    <div class="flex flex-row gap-8 justify-center mb-8 items-center">
        {% for link in links %}
            <a href="{{ link.url }}">
                <svg class="w-[36px] fill-white {{ link.classes }}" role="img" viewBox="0 0 28 28"
                     xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <title>{{ link.title }}</title>
                    {{ link.inner }}
                </svg>
            </a>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</div>
<div class="w-screen h-max bg-cover bg-center w-screen flex flex-col items-center py-8"
     style="background-image: url('{{ sectionBackgroundImg }}')">
    <div id="about" class="flex flex-col justify-start items-center px-12 gap-8 max-w-3xl mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl">About</h1>
        <img class="w-100 rounded-md" src="{{ aboutImg }}" alt="band-clubhouse"/>
        <p class="text-md leading-7 max-w-3xl">
            Mishy is an alt rock band based out of San Diego, California. Chris (vocals/sax) and
            Lawrence (drums/vocals), friends from their college days in the UCSD Pepband, reunited in 2022 with a
            simple idea: "Let's make some music together." And joined by Mike Reyes (guitar/vocals) and Mike Vargo
            (bass), that's exactly what they did, with their debut album releasing in October 2025.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div id="band" class="flex flex-col justify-start items-center px-12 gap-8 max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-3xl">The Band</h1>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[repeat(2,_24rem)] gap-8">
            {% for member in members %}
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <img class="w-100 rounded-md mb-4" src="{{ member.img }}" alt="{{ member.name }}"/>
                    <h3 class="text-xl mb-1">{{ member.name }}</h3>
                    <h4 class="text-lg mb-2">{{ member.role }}</h4>
                    <p class="text-md leading-7">{{ member.bio }}</p>
                </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
